cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.LG 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with variations in visual factors in person re-identification. 
2. cs.GR (Graphics) is also likely as the paper introduces a large-scale synthetic data engine for generating 3D person models. 
3. cs.MM (Multimedia) is another possible category as the paper deals with analyzing the influence of pedestrian rotation angle on re-ID accuracy. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper discusses the fundamental problems in person re-ID and provides insights for future practical usage. 
5. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also a possible category as the paper involves training and analyzing a re-ID system.
